to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"internet company Tencent\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"video\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"demand\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"short videos\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Television broadcasts will be available on the Sports Leisure Channel of Beijing Radio and Television Station, the Five-Star Sport News Channel of Shanghai Media Group, and Guangdong TV Sports Channel (excluding new media platforms).\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong_Television\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.554069533629275e-19, \"text\": \"Guangdong TV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong_Television\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Television broadcasts\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sports Leisure Channel\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"Beijing Radio\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"Television Station\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"the Five-Star Sport News Channel\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"Shanghai Media Group\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"new media platforms\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CMG will also collaborate with China Film Group Corporation to offer live viewing services for the Paris Olympics in select theaters nationwide.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Film_Group_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Film Group Corporation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Film_Group_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Film_Group_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"live viewing services\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"select theaters\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Except for the above authorized partners, no organization or individual may use the audio and video content or related broadcast signals of the Games without authorization from CMG.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the above authorized partners\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"no organization\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"individual\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"the audio and video content\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"related broadcast signals\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"authorization\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes, but is not limited to, live broadcasts, delayed broadcasts, on-demand services, carousels, editing, animated images, video downloads, theater screenings, or public place broadcasts.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"live broadcasts\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"delayed broadcasts\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"demand\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"carousels\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"editing\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"animated images\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"video downloads\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"theater screenings\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"public place broadcasts\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unauthorized use across various platforms, including television, radio, the Internet, mobile communication networks, IPTV, Internet TV, mobile media TV and application software, as well as accounts and mini-programs on these platforms, is prohibited in the Chinese mainland and MSAR.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2171, \"end\": 2187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999971628530376, \"rank\": 2.8371550811108086e-06, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Unauthorized use\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"various platforms\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"radio\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"the Internet\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"mobile communication networks\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"IPTV\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"Internet TV\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"mobile media TV and application software\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"accounts\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"mini\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"programs\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"these platforms\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"MSAR\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, it is prohibited to use CMG's programs for the Games or engage in any form of unfair competition under the guise of live broadcasts, rebroadcasts, or Olympic media cooperation.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"any form\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"unfair competition\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"the guise\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"live broadcasts\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"rebroadcasts\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic media cooperation\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes, but is not limited to, covert marketing activities exploiting Olympic media rights.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"covert marketing activities\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic media rights\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CMG has launched a special copyright protection campaign and will collaborate with various parties to strengthen rights protection efforts.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9998536379657099, \"rank\": 0.0001462316485986767, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a special copyright protection campaign\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"various parties\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"rights protection efforts\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Effective legal measures will be taken to crack down on infringements of the 2024 Paris Olympic Games program copyright and the use of program resources for unfair competition.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Effective legal measures\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"infringements\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic Games program copyright\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"program resources\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"unfair competition\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The legal responsibilities of relevant entities will be thoroughly investigated and enforced according to the law.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The legal responsibilities\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"relevant entities\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram